<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><title>nǐ men de shēng mìng shì shén me 迦南1242</title>
<lyrics>[V1]
 nǐ men de shēng mìng shì shén me, nǐ men de shēng mìng shì shén me?
 yuán lái shì yī piàn yún wù, chū xiàn shǎo shí jiù xiāo méi.
 nǐ men zhǐ dāng shuō zhǔ ruò yuàn yì, wǒ men jiù kě yǐ huó zhe.
 yě kě yǐ zuò zhè shì huò zuò nà shì, měi tiān dōu kào zhǔ de ēn diǎn guò.
 bù yào zhāng kuáng kuā kǒu, zhè yàng kuā kǒu dōu shì è.
 rèn shì zì jǐ shì rú cǐ yǒu xiàn, rén de shēng mìng zhǔ zhǎng wò.</lyrics>
<author>lǚ xiǎo mǐn</author>
<hymn_number>1242</hymn_number>
</song>